article_id:2501,category_name:News,title_name:3rd Anniversary Packs Are Here!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/345da88a83a404f3515589d1041cb6c1.png,message:<div>Anniversary packs are available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632722400"></span>!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/345da88a83a404f3515589d1041cb6c1.png"></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632722400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1635487199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Check out the details for each pack below.</div><div><br></div><div>■Anniversary Diamantium Mega-Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・5,700 (3,920 + 1,780 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>■Anniversary Unbind Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for unbinding weapons, wyrmprints, and dragons, as well as items useful for unlocking mana circles.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・4,800 (3,920 + 880 bonus)</div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Knight&#39;s Testament &times; 1</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1</div><div>・Rainbow Orb &times; 20</div><div>・Damascus Ingot &times; 1</div><div>・Adamantite Ingot &times; 1</div><div>・Golden Key &times; 1</div><div>・Sunlight Stone &times; 1</div><div><br></div><div>■Anniversary 5★ Dragon Voucher Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium, a voucher to summon a 5★ dragon, and items useful for upgrading dragons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・1,500 (1,200 + 300 bonus)</div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・5★ Summon Voucher+ (Dragon) &times; 1</div><div>・Succulent Dragonfruit &times; 30</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・The lineup for the 5★ Summon Voucher+ (Dragon) will be updated on occasion. For information on which dragons are available to summon, see the &quot;5★ Dragon Appearance Rates&quot; section of the 5★ Dragon Summon+ screen.</div><div>・The lineup for the 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) will not be updated.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For information about each pack, select the Shop on the Home page, then select Anniversary Packs.</div><div>2. Each Anniversary pack may only be purchased once during the availability period.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1632722400,update_time1632207636